@Node BBSArt_Intro
@{u}Real Intro@{uu}

 Okay my mate borrowed a modem from his work (he's a PC support Analyst, but
hates Pee Cee's). I got on to a BBS (Punters) I offered to do some scanning
for the sysops clients for free.  He told me to do an ANSI ad and gave me a
shareware ANSI drawing package called BBSDraw.

 Maybe I missed something but I wasn't impressed (sorry to whoever wrote
it!), so I decided to write one myself & this it.



                                @{"More about me",Link BBSArt_Intro2}
