@Node BBSArt_Install
@{u}BBSArt Install@{uu}

   Dead easy copy contents of the fonts directory to your fonts directory.

   You can copy the file BBSArt.config to your s: directory but you don't
have as the program create a default config file.  @{b}The default config is
NTSC so if your a PAL user edit it, or install the one supplied.@{ub}

   If your a PAL user this should read:
                              @{b}SCREENMODE=PAL@{ub}


